divs: Sighting DetailsIn the past few months we have taken photos of the sky in front of our house and a few of them had apparent UFOs. So we continue to take pictures in the same general area from time to time in the hope that we can photograph more UFOs. Today was one of those lucky days. The picture OVNI3 was taken around midday, OVNI1 and OVNI2 at 4PM, and OVNI4 at 4.30PM.

Summary: Took several pictures and saw objects only after downloading in the computer.
